8.11	Andre_Bauer	André Bauer	Rudolph Andreas "André" Bauer (born March 20, 1969) was the 87th Lieutenant Governor of South Carolina from 2003 to 2011. He is a member of the Republican Party. Bauer was a member of the South Carolina House of Representatives (1996–1999) and a member of the South Carolina State Senate (1999–2003), before being inaugurated as South Carolina's 87th lieutenant governor on January 15, 2003.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/AndreBauerProfile.jpg/200px-AndreBauerProfile.jpg
